及均衡實質總產出的影響。必須以圖形及文字說明否則不計分。（20 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:37:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7948d6976ec8", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111150", "c": "507", "s": "1111", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、民航人員考試、國際經濟商務人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "aboriginal", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
